                     <interp inst="t18310407-230-person1624" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prosecutor's errand boy - the bell rang; I came down to a boy, and left the door open, but I did not see the prisoner - I knew the flute was in the parlour.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming across Smithfield - a gentleman came up, and asked me to carry these things to the Angel, at Islington - I thought he was behind me at the time.</p>
